            <title><![CDATA[Supreme Court preserves access to widely used abortion pill, while lawsuit plays out]]></title>
            <link>https://www.pbs.org/newshour/nation/supreme-court-preserves-access-to-widely-used-abortion-pill-while-lawsuit-plays-out</link>
